{"tid":2446284,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"出道1854天奪一位　「奇蹟女團」Brave Girls爆哭：差點解散","createTime":"2021-03-14T10:40:49.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-15T05:48:41.000Z","uid":16659,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"bb514fdc1f8b55b6efc0fa34a60e8f68fa7639cc","tid":2446284,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-14T10:40:49.000Z","msg":"南韓時下最夯女團Brave Girls拿下一位！團體於2011年成軍，2016年又歷經成員改組，歌壇之路卻走得相當艱辛，直到近期才因為4年前的主打歌《Rollin&rsquo;》重新爆紅，僅剩的4位成員被音樂節目召回，終於在14日拿下演藝生涯中第一個一位殊榮，她們感動到爆哭：「面臨解散危機，也從來沒想過可以重新站上舞台。」一番話逼哭歌迷。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/5503/d5503537.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F5503%2Fd5503537.jpg&h=cbd5c9d2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲▼出道1854天奪一位，Brave Girls爆哭。（圖／翻攝自SBS）<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/5503/d5503534.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F5503%2Fd5503534.jpg&h=455ace31&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nBrave Girls近期被召回音樂節目打歌，團體改組後的出道1854天以來，終於在14日拿下一位，4人震驚到摀著嘴巴，玟瑩發表感言：「面臨解散危機，從來沒想過可以重新站上舞台，謝謝大家給予這麼多愛意，還有謝謝成員撐下來了。」侑廷也哭著說：「當大家都說不行的時候，謝謝仍然相信我們、等著我們的製作人勇敢兄弟，公司同僚、國軍士兵們謝謝。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/5503/d5503536.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F5503%2Fd5503536.jpg&h=077fc94c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲「奇蹟女團」Brave Girls現在是南韓時下討論度最高的女團。（圖／翻攝自SBS）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nBrave Girls於2017年發行的歌曲《Rollin》引起各界暴動，中毒性的旋律、性感撩人的舞蹈，令軍中阿兵哥著迷不已，她們睽違4年被重新召回音樂節目表演，其中，成員侑廷微肉的身材與甜美笑眼融化大批男性，個人鏡頭的影片吸引76萬點擊，留言處充滿禁止她減肥的要求，「禁止姐姐減肥，希望不要因為看到那些人的留言就走心」、「不准勇兄要求她們減肥，Brave Girls現在不是你的是全國民的」，足見她的火紅人氣。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=GoBLWClS4ts\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DGoBLWClS4ts&d=wSR7%2FpLLUFbraZn9MQiPfFNDr8uFEZb%2F0ofPPvrEBCw%3D&h=5d8215be\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=GoBLWClS4ts</a>"},{"pid":"d91939e9a4fd9198771254e4874f3ff30e865cda","tid":2446284,"uid":91833,"like":3,"dislike":12,"score":-9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-14T10:44:35.000Z","msg":"韓國女明星條條女差唔多樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8490fda81afb004126c4ff52348698437c6fa5ed","tid":2446284,"uid":272819,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-03-14T10:44:48.000Z","msg":"好開心 <br />\n依個世界真係有奇蹟<br />\n但可惜stellar冇依個機會了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c7cc6348ca6b1e64716701c9d2f3d4b4f618ea6","tid":2446284,"uid":261849,"like":3,"dislike":11,"score":-8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-14T10:58:34.000Z","msg":"成隊一樣樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"01185dc256e4043834b737b05afa62bf7acc41ec","tid":2446284,"uid":89931,"like":18,"dislike":1,"score":17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-14T11:02:52.000Z","msg":"諗唔到樓上咁多人衝出嚟同人講自己係盲嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"80e866e263d68b4b79a1167ba9e58898574f3756","tid":2446284,"uid":211461,"like":1,"dislike":5,"score":-4,"quote":{"pid":"4c7cc6348ca6b1e64716701c9d2f3d4b4f618ea6","tid":2446284,"uid":261849,"like":3,"dislike":11,"score":-8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-14T10:58:34.000Z","msg":"成隊一樣樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-14T11:19:21.000Z","msg":"幅圖左下同後中個樣一樣<br />\n後左個樣似momo 怪物嗰隻momo<br />\n後右個鼻so fake"},{"pid":"b6ed022d47d682a73c059f4051ebf51c193c046a","tid":2446284,"uid":68678,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-14T11:32:15.000Z","msg":"其實真係好普通"},{"pid":"c41270c37d5146cc4087a6f4e15cc31799167c95","tid":2446284,"uid":3117